    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集、合成、战斗!　用你生产的物品赢得胜利! </h2>这是为那些日常没有时间，但喜欢 &quot;收集、合成和战斗 &quot;的人创造的游戏。<br><br>游戏提供了一个平滑的进展和具有挑战性的战斗。<br><br>总的游戏时间约为15小时。<br><br><br><strong>收集</strong>。<br>首先，积攒资金以扩大你的农场。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/485ff4b4b9e3393574a091a649787d49.poster.avif?t=1645160778\" width=404 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/485ff4b4b9e3393574a091a649787d49.webm?t=1645160778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/485ff4b4b9e3393574a091a649787d49.mp4?t=1645160778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>合成</strong>。<br>一旦你积攒了足够的钱来购买配方，你就可以把它与你在农场、田野或地牢中收集的物品结合起来<br>创造你自己的物品。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/912dabd05706f6874ca4189a9f73af81.poster.avif?t=1645160778\" width=404 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/912dabd05706f6874ca4189a9f73af81.webm?t=1645160778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/912dabd05706f6874ca4189a9f73af81.mp4?t=1645160778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>战斗</strong>。<br>在这个游戏中没有普通的攻击。你用合成的物品进行攻击。物品也被用来恢复。特殊动作也被用来治疗和给予buff和debuffs。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/9ba22c096d2b965d94752ca64f101992.poster.avif?t=1645160778\" width=404 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/9ba22c096d2b965d94752ca64f101992.webm?t=1645160778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/9ba22c096d2b965d94752ca64f101992.mp4?t=1645160778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>敌人的攻击是非常严重的，如果你在战斗开始后的三个回合内什么都不做，你就会输。你合成的每种物品都有独特的能力，如状态调整和异常，所以在战斗中要充分利用它们。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/7a32479fa02f84d052d4f16cee2dc0e7.webp?t=1645160778\" width=31 height=31 /></span>钉子<br>　增加物理攻击，减少物理防御。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/e5a70a4cb457d941a4fc10aa4b29bb9a.webp?t=1645160778\" width=30 height=31 /></span>火属性<br>　增加魔法攻击，减少魔法防御。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/ab728793fbb1eeae27376d9f60cd4480.webp?t=1645160778\" width=31 height=30 /></span>水属性<br>　减少物理攻击，增加物理防御。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/111d1ff4782973d74739442b334f95dd.webp?t=1645160778\" width=32 height=30 /></span>冰属性<br>　减少魔法攻击并增加魔法攻击<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/702a5b4da6da51c9250526d66ce7211d.webp?t=1645160778\" width=30 height=30 /></span>土<br>　增加敏捷度或减少敏捷度<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/bdcc9aee1ae9bd1ae7d5dcc24353babe.webp?t=1645160778\" width=30 height=31 /></span>风<br>　减缓对手的回合顺序，同时给予敏捷降低。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/482e957808e4631e64b835b7dc5e5640.webp?t=1645160778\" width=31 height=31 /></span>烹饪<br>　每回合提供状态异常恢复、特殊攻击量恢复和HP恢复。<br><br>战斗将是主动时间的战斗，回合数以敏捷速度为准。<br>有许多物品可以调整你的敏捷速度，所以请调整你的敏捷，以推进对你有利的战斗。<br><br>请享受一对一的战斗，而不是一对多的战斗。<br><br><strong>地牢探索</strong>。<br>一共有七个地牢，有十二个等级，老板是强大的敌人。<br>物品是有限的，所以如果你只使用最强的物品，最终的游戏会很困难。<br>在地牢中拾取和生产物品，同时有时要从地牢中跑出来，才能进入下一关。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/4026b05741ced0b8c8c417e1312708e6.poster.avif?t=1645160778\" width=404 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/4026b05741ced0b8c8c417e1312708e6.webm?t=1645160778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1838660/extras/4026b05741ced0b8c8c417e1312708e6.mp4?t=1645160778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>故事</strong>。<br>没有太多的故事，但主角必须征服总共七个地牢，才能到达魔王的城堡。<br>随着故事的发展，你能得到的物品也逐渐变好。",
